ow, but others face strong headwinds\">{{cite news|title= Africa Outlook: Ethiopian Airlines and Air Mauritius grow, but others face strong headwinds|publisher= CAPA Centre for Aviation|date= 3 June 2016|url= http://centreforaviation.com/analysis/africa-outlook-ethiopian-airlines-and-air-mauritius-grow-but-others-face-strong-headwinds-282282|url-status= dead|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20160731164133/http://centreforaviation.com/analysis/africa-outlook-ethiopian-airlines-and-air-mauritius-grow-but-others-face-strong-headwinds-282282|archivedate= 31 July 2016}}&nbsp;</ref>\n<!-- + -->\n<ref name=\"FI1985-120\">{{cite journal|title= World airline directory\u2014South African Airways|journal= [[Flight International]]|issn= 0015-3710|volume= 127|issue= 3953|date= 30 March 1985|page= 120|url= https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1985/1985%20-%200980.html|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180221185956/https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1985/1985%20-%200980.html|archive-date= 21 February 2018}}</ref>\n<!-- + -->\n<ref name=\"FI1998-87\">{{cite journal|title= World airline directory\u2014South African Airways|journal= [[Flight International]]|issn= 0015-3710|date= 1\u20137 April 1998|volume= 153|issue= 4619|page= 87|url= https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1998/1998%20-%200879.html|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180228160333/https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1998/1998%20-%200879.html|archive-date= 28 February 2018}}</ref>\n<!-- + -->\n<ref name=\"International_Timetable\">{{cite web|title= International Timetable|publisher= South African Airways|date= January 2020|url= https://www.flysaa.com/documents/51855150/276053604/Our+Flights_JAN+2020.pdf/|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200126135559/https://www.flysaa.com/documents/51855150/276053604/Our+Flights_JAN+2020.pdf/|archive-date= 26 January 2020}}</ref>\n<!-- + -->\n<ref name=\"SAA celebrates 50 Years of direct flights between South Africa and